<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062994-0146 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 055920 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 29, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
