</P>
<P>
 Status: The Santa Clarita Planning Commission approved the project on Tuesday. 
Approval is still needed from the Santa Clarita City Council. 
</P>
<P>
 Amenities: Includes some neighborhood parks, a 27-acre business park, an 
elementary school and preserves 450 acres of open space. The Newhall Ranch 
Project 
</P>
<P>
 Projected population: 70,000. 
</P>
